::Feline::

She walked to the entrance of the ship. She opened up her 
commlink,"Zardus, we are off to complete the mission. Please do not 
have the other shoot us down. It would be appreciated,"she 
paused,"handsomebot."

She closed her link and looked at Skulletron.  You'd better let me go 
into the base first. If we both went in there at the same time, they 
might get suspicious.  I'll go in first and you come in in an hour or 
two after that. OK Sweetbot?"
